data.description: Welcome home to this stunning farmhouse-style home situated on 0.61 acres!  This 4 bedroom, 3 full bath with bonus room, has it all! One Level living at its finest!  Primary plus 2 bedrooms located on the first level! Enjoy the rocking chair front porch. Entertaining in the open concept first floor! The gourmet kitchen has a large island with granite and plenty of room to sit, and a large pantry!  Family room has a beautiful stone fireplace,  built-ins and a cathedral ceiling!  Shiplap throughout the first floor adds to the farmhouse feel!  The first floor primary bedroom has shiplap accent wall and accent ceiling!   Step into your spa-like, beautifully tiled primary bath with walk-in rain shower!  2 large closets top it off!  Enjoy the huge  fenced in backyard, with 8' privacy fence, from the screened in porch!  Hang out in the 44x14 workshop (could be your he/she shed!) with electric/AC!  Garden in the greenhouse!  Don't miss this amazing home!
